text: TL-599, also known as SB-8, is an extremely potent carbamate acetylcholinesterase inhibitor. ==See also== *Neostigmine *Miotine *T-1123 *TL-1238 *Physostigmine ==References== Category:Acetylcholinesterase inhibitors Category:Aromatic carbamates Category:Quaternary ammonium compounds Category:Phenol esters Category:Isopropyl compounds Category:Iodides
